%F A387736 a(n) = Sum_{k=ceiling(n/2)..n} b(n-k,k-2) = Sum_{k=0..floor(n/2)} b(k,n-k-2) where b(0,k)=1, b(n,k) = b(n,k-1) + b(n-k, k-2) and b(n,k)=0 if n<0 or k<2.
